{"tid":824331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班仆街抵比人笑港奴","createTime":"2018-09-17T04:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T04:53:29.000Z","uid":72484,"like":72,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d79c050da6b703f0faf0283c06ba91cc88376a80","tid":824331,"uid":72484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T04:46:20.000Z","msg":"明知無巴士，狗鐵唔係全通，咁多站逼出閘口，都仲可以堅持排隊繼續返工，返得黎都準備收工啦<br />\n<br />\n唔返一日半日洗死咩，呢d時勢仲比老闆/HR話既，都擺明係閪工啦，堅持你一定要開工既，咪home office囉，駛唔駛哂時間搏曬命一定要返到公司呀<br />\n<br />\n個政府咁撚on9，你地又陪佢癲，一個願打一個願捱，搞到自己咁低賤，唔壓榨你地都對唔住自己啦<br />\n<br />\n比d志氣啦香港人，唔好再用獅子山精神打飛機作賤自己啦好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：一早whatsapp左呀頭話唔返，藍剔左，理撚得佢，訓到岩岩先醒"},{"pid":"f94dc6a7e5c09ca6e3085bb44a17912d9ef43ff7","tid":824331,"uid":72484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T04:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7e068e60518d0478e325cc309f47ca583383a5","tid":824331,"uid":72484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T04:49:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bc55f4f0830f742c3dffb1f9f86454fc8ce126","tid":824331,"uid":169310,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T04:52:11.000Z","msg":"我真係諗唔到仲有咩可以阻到港豬返工，香港世界第一！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/125151_c9a8b5dfd8f3acb9c4ac71e3589256a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F125151_c9a8b5dfd8f3acb9c4ac71e3589256a6.png&h=55277355&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/125151_31ceb08fd79343370dc35797fc83834c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F125151_31ceb08fd79343370dc35797fc83834c.png&h=b30a4b44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bca79db73e659ea333fed37f670568ac8465feb","tid":82